A Registry of DICOM Unique Identifiers (UIDs) (Normative)

Table A-1 lists the UID values that are registered and used throughout the Parts of the DICOM Standard. This central registry ensures that when additional UIDs are assigned, non-duplicate values are assigned. For retired UIDs, the edition of the Standard in parentheses is the edition in which the item last appeared before it was retired.
